VALUES
  ('Pepper Spray', 'An ergonomically driven pepper spray concept that is pocket-sized, quickly accessible, intuitive, and reduces user error. My concept was inspired by the Star Wars'' ship "the Millenium Falcon", and is meant to be magnetically clipped outside of a user''s pocket. Users can remove the apparatus via a magnetic switch and use the side triggers to dispel the spray liquid. When the liquid is dispelled, it triggers LED and audio signals to further alarm a potential attacker.', 'This project exemplifies the IYA mindset because it represents the messy, iterative process of product design and development. As innovative thinkers, we''re often tasked to consider the user throughout our ideation processes, which drive the form and function of the projects we develop.', 'Michael Steele', '');
